<?php

use Dodopayments\Client;
use Dodopayments\Models\EventType;
use Dodopayments\Models\PatchWebhookRequest;

$input = new Models\PatchWebhookRequest(
  description: "description",
  disabled: true,
  filterTypes: [],
  metadata: [],
  rateLimit: 5,
  url: "url"
);

  input: $input,
  webhookId: "webhook_id"
);

print_r($response);
